    <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/hero/1920/800" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30" />
    <div class="relative text-center px-4 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">Radiant Skin Starts Here</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-6">Premium supplements, honest prices – message us on WhatsApp.</p>
